==English==
===Etymology===
From the name of the inventor, [[w:Robert Atkins|Robert Atkins]].

===Noun phrase===
'''Atkins™ diet''' 

#(''with'' '''the''') A [[diet]] in which a person loses weight by reducing the intake of [[carbohydrate]]s, instead obtaining energy from [[dietary]] and stored [[fat]].
#:''I've lost ten pounds since I started the Atkins diet''

